---
title: Warm Tilapia Poke-Style Bowls with Corn, Cabbage and Spicy Mayo
description: We're making some changes to a beloved bowl style and upping the heat (just a little!) to create a warm version. This dish features all the fresh elements of the poke bowl, along with the addition of tasty fish and charred corn.
